{"id":"2418abdb-d3df-4b98-90f0-bd6c5b6c12d6","name":"Any-RPG | Create your Story!","description":"<h2 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 186, 0)\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 209, 85)\">Update v1.1</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 186, 0)\">&gt;&gt;</span></h2><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 41)\">F</span><span style=\"color: rgb(30, 255, 67)\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(72, 255, 101)\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 255, 139)\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 255, 178)\">-</span><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 255, 190)\">W</span><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 255, 207)\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(171, 255, 185)\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(134, 255, 154)\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(65, 255, 95)\">d</span> bot!</h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>What the world is like is entirely up to you! Create your own story or put yourself into an existing one. The only limit is your imagination!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #ff1010\"><u>I recommend using DeepSeek or any other proxy for better responses and a more flexible enviroment.</u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 90, 255)\"><strong>&lt;&lt;&lt;</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(166, 166, 255)\"><strong>Features</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(90, 90, 255)\"><strong>&gt;&gt;&gt;</strong></span></h1><ul><li><p><em>Formatted dialogue (inner thoughts included) </em>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 85, 212)\">v1.0</span>]</p></li><li><p><em>Formatted narration </em>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 85, 212)\">v1.0</span>]</p></li><li><p><em>Full control over the narrator's personality (informal and objective by default) </em>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 85, 212)\">v1.0</span>]</p></li><li><p><em>Ability to communicate with the narrator, {{char}}, directly (you can alter elements inside the story this way) </em>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 85, 212)\">v1.0</span>]</p></li><li><p><em>Real-time narration of events</em> [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 209, 85)\">v1.1</span>]</p></li></ul>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"pFnj9cQhxgI-rdOL3JNOK.webp","creator":"TheInaccessibleCardinal","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":5319,"messages":227706,"created_at":"2025-06-21T15:32:09.981625+00:00"}